      "Target class: SeaLake\n",
      "Top-5 retrieved images:\n",
      "  1.                 Forest | cosine=0.2833 | relevant=False | path=/Users/tienesng06/Desktop/ACIVS_ThayBach/data/EuroSAT_MS/Forest/Forest_527.tif\n",
